Package: fqtkWrapper
Title: R package wrapper around the command-line tool 'fqtk', developed by Fulcrum Genomics.
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Moritz", "Broft", , "moritz.broft@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides an R wrapper around the command-line tool 'fqtk', developed by
    Fulcrum Genomics, for working with FASTQ files. This package allows users to integrate
    fqtk functionality directly into R workflows. If you use 'fqtk' or this wrapper in your
    work, please cite the original tool as: Homer et al. (2024) <https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.13345414>.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Config/rextendr/version: 0.4.1.9000
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.2)
